          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1599495338101-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1599495338101-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the<strong> salad </strong>to a bowl with your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>balsamic salad</strong></p><p>Serve the pizza with the <strong>balsamic salad </strong>on top or to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
